snippet.title: Best VGM 1986 - Dragon Quest - Chateau Ladutorm (Tantegel Castle)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 563 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TXO9vzXnAeg

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Dragon Quest / Warrior (1986)
Chateau Ladutorm (Tantegel Castle)
Koichi Sugiyama
